RACE.RACE_TEXT: NORTH DAKOTA HORSE PARK RACE 1 5 1/2F Dirt CR: 26. Maiden Special Weight Purse 5250. FOR NORTH DAKOTA BRED MAIDENS, THREE YEARS OLD AND OLDER. Three Year Olds, 124 lbs.; Older, 126 lbs.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: BABY YATTA early advantage, drew off. ROADSTAR KING bided time, came on late. LENNOX THE GREAT mid-pack early, no improvement. P K'S PEANUT toiled, minor reward. JERRY TIME competed early, backed up.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: NORTH DAKOTA HORSE PARK RACE 2 5 1/2F Dirt CR: 47. Allowance Purse 5500. FOR THREE YEARS OLD AND OLDER WHICH HAVE NEVER WON THREE RACES. Three Year Olds, 124 lbs.; Older, 126 lbs.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: CHAMA inside, seized lead 3/8p, opened up. MISSEN THE POINT bid, repelled. MARIAHS STAR saved inside, modest run. GOLDEN STAR ROCK 4 wide 3/16p, late run. SCOOTER FLASH back early, no late response.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: NORTH DAKOTA HORSE PARK RACE 3 4 1/2F Dirt CR: 77. Allowance Purse 6500. FOR FILLIES AND MARES THREE YEARS OLD AND OLDER. Three Year Olds, 124 lbs.; Older, 126 lbs.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: OUR PETUNIA surged in final 1/8, up in time. MISS WILDCAT led, overtaken very late. SHARP CONTRAST 3 wide rally 3/16p. FLAMING INDY battled early, backed up. A BUNCH FOR LUNCH raced wide, no late effort. GIGGLEBOX in wake of others.

ENTRY.NAME: Our Petunia
ENTRY.COMMENT: surged in final 1/8, up in time

RACE.RACE_TEXT: NORTH DAKOTA HORSE PARK RACE 4 4F Dirt CR: 80. Claiming Purse 4250. FOR THREE YEARS OLD AND OLDER. Three Year Olds, 118 lbs.; Older, 121 lbs. Claiming Price $1,500, For Each $500 Higher In Claiming Price An Additional 1 lb.
